node.text: “What you call the thinker is simply your thought of yourself. The thinker is a thought among thoughts” Alan Watts
“The moment you truly realize that all forms are unstable, a deep peace arises from within”
You can only think clearly when you have the ability to not think 🤔
the unobserved mind is the ego
The moment you allow the condition (internal or external) - you have transcended it. You have become the consciousness in which the condition appears.
